1
00:00:00,584 --> 00:00:02,128
Oh, that's a depressing site.
哦 那真是个令人伤心的地方

2
00:00:02,168 --> 00:00:04,216
Hage's been mentally sound for all these years.
哈格这些年的精神状态很好

3
00:00:04,224 --> 00:00:07,976
Then he spends a few months in Tokyo and he's completely lost his mind.
然后他去东京待了几个月 就完全失去了理智

4
00:00:08,680 --> 00:00:10,864
Tokyo's a strange place, Tamasaburo.
东京是个非常奇怪的地方 大阪

5
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:12,880
I don't understand the people here at all.
我一点都理解不了这里的人

6
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:17,240
If we would execute Operation Specter on Shikoku Island, it would have worked beautifully
如果我们在四国岛上执行 幽灵行动 会完成得更好

7
00:00:18,008 --> 00:00:20,240
Offerings at our temple would have tripled.
我们寺庙的贡品会有三倍多

8
00:00:20,808 --> 00:00:24,390
Master Kincho, please take me back with you to Shikoku Island,
金鸟大师 求您带我一起回四国岛吧

9
00:00:24,488 --> 00:00:26,400
and train me to follow in your footsteps.
并且训练我跟随您的脚步

10
00:00:26,688 --> 00:00:28,392
There's nothing I would value more.
已经没有什么我会更看重的了

11
00:00:29,944 --> 00:00:33,088
- I see, Tamasaburo. - Yes.
-我知道了 大阪 -在

12
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:36,280
Do you honestly wish to become my successor?
你真的想成为我的继承者吗

13
00:00:36,576 --> 00:00:38,096
Yes, Master Kincho.
是的 金鸟大师

14
00:00:38,344 --> 00:00:40,550
I've been hoping you would say that.
我一直希望你可以这么说

15
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:43,504
However, you must assure me
但是 你必须向我保证

16
00:00:43,912 --> 00:00:46,392
that you're not making a selfish decision.
你不会做自私的决定

17
00:00:46,456 --> 00:00:50,080
and abandoning your fellow raccoons just to get back to my daughter.
为了回到我女儿的身边而抛弃你的狸猫伙伴

18
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:52,560
- Are you? - Of course not, Master.
-你会吗 -当然不会了 大师

19
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,272
- Only. - Only what? Tell me.
-只不过 -只不过什么 告诉我

20
00:00:57,640 --> 00:01:00,728
Even you Master Kincho have lost the support of the other raccoons.
甚至是金鸟大师你都失去了其他狸猫的支持

21
00:01:01,120 --> 00:01:03,360
So what good can we achieve by staying here?
所以我们待在这能有什么好处呢

22
00:01:03,540 --> 00:01:05,896
There is something. Come with me.
有点东西要给你看 跟我来


